---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
    <div class="min-h-screen bg-base-200 pt-24 px-6">
        <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
            <h1
                class="text-5xl font-bold text-primary mb-8 gsap-reveal gsap-up"
            >
                Work Experience
            </h1>

            <div class="mb-10 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-base-100 p-6 gsap-reveal gsap-up">
                <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">
                    No professional job experience yet.
                </p>
                <p class="text-base-content/70 leading-relaxed">
                    This page is used to show practical project work, technical growth, and the kinds of systems I have been building while preparing for an AI engineer role.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-8">
                <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl gsap-reveal gsap-up">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h2 class="card-title text-2xl">Meguri</h2>
                        <p class="text-sm text-base-content/60">
                            Personal project • AI / Inventory / Forecasting
                        </p>
                        <p class="mt-4">
                            Building a workspace-scoped smart stock platform for recipe-based businesses and small retail, with inventory management, recipe/BOM mapping, supplier planning, alerts, and forecasting.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl gsap-reveal gsap-up">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h2 class="card-title text-2xl">Portfolio & Learning Projects</h2>
                        <p class="text-sm text-base-content/60">
                            Personal projects • Full stack / AI-focused work
                        </p>
                        <p class="mt-4">
                            Built projects such as NextMart, BookCube, and Kitchen Inventory to strengthen full-stack engineering, data modeling, and product thinking while moving toward AI engineer roles.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
